QuestData.Title: Voices of the Eternal
QuestData.Description:
<Bolvar peers at the grand figures before him, at the numberless gateways stretching out into the ether.>
This chamber is... truly wondrous.
Yet there is no time to be awestruck. The Honored Voice must begin this meeting at once.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to the Enclave in Oribos.
QuestData.RewardText:
The Winter Queen must be the Jailer's next target.
We must do all we can to protect her.
And I have a few ideas how we can do that...

Objectives.Objective: Return to the Enclave in Oribos
